(1476, 'LLCFC1', 'Predicted to be involved in fusion of sperm to egg plasma membrane involved in single fertilization. Predicted to be located in extracellular region. [provided by Alliance of Genome Resources, May 2025]', '7', 'protein_coding', 31544444, 31548427, 49.67, 6, 'ENSG00000165131', 'Q96L11'),
